				<A href="/geography/default.asp?MAPID=1416">Nektulos Forest</a><br>
				
				<A href="/geography/default.asp?MAPID=1472">West Commonlands</a><br>
				
				</font>
				<br><br>
				<font face="verdana" size="3">
				<p><b>Faction Hits:</b></font>
				<font face="verdana" size="2">
				<u><b>Worse</b></u><br></font>
				<font face="verdana" size="1">
				None<br>
				</font>
				<br>
				<font face="verdana" size="2">
				<u><b>Better</b></u><br></font><font face="verdana" size="1">
				None<br>
				</font>
				<br>
				</p></td>
		  </tr>
		  <tr>
		    <td colspan="3" width="100%" align="center">
		    <font face="verdana" size="2">Probably the toughest of all bears in Norrath, this one easily beats the grizzly in size and strength.  They are found in certain forest and plains zones, and unless you are at least level 14, you'll not want to attempt to solo one of these.  They offer good experience, and the loot is not too bad either.</font></td>
		  </tr>
		  <tr>
		    <td colspan="3" width="100%">
		    <font face="verdana" size="2">Submitted by: <A href="mailto:">Ipsidack</a></font></td>
		  </tr>
		</table><br><br>
		<font face="verdana" size="2"><a href="../UserUpdate.asp?id=2180">
		[Add Comments] Please Add your comments here!</a></font><br><hr>


	</td>
	<td width="1%">&nbsp;</td>
</tr>
